sp_scores.title: Defeat the Materia Keeper without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: When the Materia Keeper's HP drops low enough, it uses Cura and a powerful spell called Trine, kupo! Use your abilities sparingly and save them for when it starts using Cura, then finish it off fast!

Temple of the Ancients - Void of Time

sp_scores.title: Defeat Lost Number without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: When Lost Number's HP drops low enough, it changes into one of two different forms, kupo. Its red form is resistant to magic, but vulnerable to physical attacks. Its purple form is vulnerable to magic, but hardened against physical attacks. Keep an eye on your magic and physical ability uses, and use the right attacks at the right time!
tip_battle.title: Lost Number
